Presentation template for High Performance Computing Course at the University of Lugano

Use xelatex (not pdflatex!) as LaTeX processor, e.g.:

/usr/local/texlive/2013/bin/x86_64-linux/xelatex -shell-escape -synctex=1 -interaction=nonstopmode %.tex

Known to work best with 2013' TexLive release downloaded from web page (not shipped with Ubuntu/Fedora distros).

